   Links to NASA's Distributed Active Archive Center Alliances and
   Cooperating Data Centers:
   Each DAAC holds and provides data pertaining to a particular earth
   science discipline, and together the DAACs provide a physically
   distributed but logically integrated database to support
   interdisciplinary global change research.

